OL,6,Fbid to replace with former player and
OL,7,FBayer Leverkusen manager Xabi Alonso
OL,8,Fhas ended in disappointment.
OL,10,FThe Spaniard has announced he will
OL,11,Fremain manager of Leverkusen next
OL,12,Fseason, with the club currently
OL,13,Funbeaten in all competitions and 10
OL,14,Fpoints ahead of Bayern Munich at the
OL,15,Ftop of the Bundesliga with eight games
OL,16,Fto play.
