OL,3,CLiverpool manager target Alonso to
OL,4,Cstay in Germany
OL,6,F"We're in a situation we have to
OL,7,Fenjoy. There are still two months to
OL,8,Fgo, it's going to be really intense
OL,9,Fand demanding, but enjoyable,
OL,10,Fhopefully. We'll go full gas for the
OL,11,Fbig goals we have ahead of us. Let's
OL,12,Fsee how far we can go, but our wish is
OL,13,Fclear."
OL,15,FThere is a chance that Leverkusen and
OL,16,FLiverpool could meet in what would be
OL,17,FKlopp's final game in charge, the
OL,18,FEuropa League final in Dublin on May
OL,19,F22, having been kept on opposite sides
OL,20,Fof the draw for the quarter and semi-
OL,21,Ffinals.
