OL,6,FWhen asked about Alonso's decision at
OL,7,Fhis own press conference, Klopp said:
OL,8,F"One part I can speak about is that
OL,9,Fhe's a young manager at a club where
OL,10,Fhe's doing really well.
OL,12,F"The club are doing an incredible job
OL,13,Fthere. Leverkusen have a good team,
OL,14,Fprobably will keep their team
OL,15,Ftogether, I think that's possible this
OL,16,Fyear as well, it's not all years like
OL,17,Fthat. So I understand that he wants to
OL,18,Fdo that. And for the other stuff (the
OL,19,Flinks to Liverpool), there's nothing I
OL,20,Fhave to say about that."
